"title": "1310: God, as judge",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "1310: god, as judge",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>As a part of his sovereignty and authority, God is executor of his righteousness within the created order. Jesus Christ shares in this ongoing work.</p>\n<h2>God has authority to judge</h2>\n<h3>God's status as judge</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps75:7\">PSA 75:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps50:6\">PSA 50:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps76:8-Ps76:9\">PSA 76:8–76:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl11:9\">ECC 11:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa33:22\">ISA 33:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa66:16\">ISA 66:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim4:8\">2TI 4:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:23\">HEB 12:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas4:12\">JAS 4:12</a></p>\n<h3>He decides disputes</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg11:27\">JDG 11:27</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen16:5\">GEN 16:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen31:53\">GEN 31:53</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam24:15\">1SA 24:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa2:4\">ISA 2:4</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic4:3\">MIC 4:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:9\">JAS 5:9</a></p>\n<h3>He presides in the heavenly court</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa3:13\">ISA 3:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps50:4\">PSA 50:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps82:1\">PSA 82:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan7:9-Dan7:10\">DAN 7:9–7:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel3:12\">JOL 3:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev20:11-Rev20:15\">REV 20:11–20:15</a></p>\n<h2>God is judge over the whole of creation</h2>\n<h3>He judges the earth</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen18:25\">GEN 18:25</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps9:8\">PSA 9:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps58:11\">PSA 58:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps82:8\">PSA 82:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps94:2\">PSA 94:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps96:13\">PSA 96:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps98:9\">PSA 98:9</a></p>\n<h3>He judges every individual</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek33:20\">EZK 33:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl3:17\">ECC 3:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb9:27\">HEB 9:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet4:5\">1PE 4:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:15\">JUD 1:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev20:12\">REV 20:12</a></p>\n<h3>He judges the nations</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel3:12\">JOL 3:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps9:19-Ps9:20\">PSA 9:19–9:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps110:6\">PSA 110:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Obad1:15\">OBA 1:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph3:8\">ZEP 3:8</a></p>\n<h3>He judges rulers of nations</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:23\">ISA 40:23</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer25:17-Jer25:27\">JER 25:17–25:27</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev6:15-Rev6:17\">REV 6:15–6:17</a></p>\n<h3>He judges his own people</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:30\">HEB 10:30</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:36\">DEU 32:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps78:62\">PSA 78:62</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer1:16\">JER 1:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet4:17\">1PE 4:17</a></p>\n<h3>He judges angels</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet2:4\">2PE 2:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:6\">JUD 1:6</a></p>\n<h3>He judges Satan</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:14-Gen3:15\">GEN 3:14–3:15</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:41\">MAT 25:41</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim3:6\">1TI 3:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev20:10\">REV 20:10</a></p>\n<h2>God's judgment is inescapable</h2>\n<h3>No-one can hide from God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Obad1:4\">OBA 1:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:8-Gen3:9\">GEN 3:8–3:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job11:20\">JOB 11:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer11:11\">JER 11:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos9:1-Amos9:4\">AMO 9:1–9:4</a></p>\n<h3>God searches human hearts</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer17:10\">JER 17:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr28:9\">1CH 28:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps7:9\">PSA 7:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov5:21\">PRO 5:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer11:20\">JER 11:20</a></p>\n<h3>God reveals secrets</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom2:16\">ROM 2:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl12:14\">ECC 12:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer16:17\">JER 16:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor4:5\">1CO 4:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb4:13\">HEB 4:13</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of God acting as judge</h2>\n<h3>His judgment of the earth in sending the flood</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen6:7\">GEN 6:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen6:13\">GEN 6:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen6:17\">GEN 6:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen7:21-Gen7:23\">GEN 7:21–7:23</a></p>\n<h3>His judgment of individuals</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen4:9-Gen4:12\">GEN 4:9–4:12</a> <em>Cain</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:3-Acts5:10\">ACT 5:3–5:10</a> <em>Ananias and Sapphira</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:8-Acts13:11\">ACT 13:8–13:11</a> <em>Elymas the sorcerer</em></p>\n<h3>His judgment of families</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh7:24-Josh7:25\">JOS 7:24–7:25</a> <em>of Achan</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam3:12-1Sam3:13\">1SA 3:12–3:13</a> <em>of Eli</em></p>\n<h3>His judgment of cities</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen19:24-Gen19:25\">GEN 19:24–19:25</a> <em>Sodom and Gomorrah</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh6:24\">JOS 6:24</a> <em>Jericho</em></p>\n<h3>His judgment of nations</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut7:1-Deut7:5\">DEU 7:1–7:5</a> <em>the Canaanite nations</em></p>\n<h3>His judgment of the rulers of nations</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr26:16-2Chr26:21\">2CH 26:16–26:21</a> <em>Uzziah</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan4:31-Dan4:33\">DAN 4:31–4:33</a> <em>Nebuchadnezzar</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan5:22-Dan5:30\">DAN 5:22–5:30</a> <em>Belshazzar</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts12:22-Acts12:23\">ACT 12:22–12:23</a> <em>Herod</em></p>\n<h3>His judgment of his own people</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg2:11-Judg2:15\">JDG 2:11–2:15</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr36:15-2Chr36:20\">2CH 36:15–36:20</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa33:22\">ISA 33:22</a></p>\n<h2>God's character is revealed through his righteous judgments</h2>\n<h3>His sovereignty</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps9:7\">PSA 9:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps96:10\">PSA 96:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps99:4\">PSA 99:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek6:14\">EZK 6:14</a></p>\n<h3>His power</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod6:6\">EXO 6:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod14:31\">EXO 14:31</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek20:33-Ezek20:36\">EZK 20:33–20:36</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev18:8\">REV 18:8</a></p>\n<h3>His holiness</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev10:1-Lev10:3\">LEV 10:1–10:3</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam6:19-1Sam6:20\">1SA 6:19–6:20</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek28:22\">EZK 28:22</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev16:5\">REV 16:5</a></p>\n<h3>His anger</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Nah1:2-Nah1:3\">NAM 1:2–1:3</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom2:5\">ROM 2:5</a></p>\n<h3>His truth</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps96:13\">PSA 96:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom2:2\">ROM 2:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev16:7\">REV 16:7</a></p>\n<h3>His impartiality</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr19:7\">2CH 19:7</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom2:9-Rom2:11\">ROM 2:9–2:11</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:25\">COL 3:25</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:17\">1PE 1:17</a></p>\n<h3>His compassion</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam3:31-Lam3:33\">LAM 3:31–3:33</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos11:8-Hos11:9\">HOS 11:8–11:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah3:10\">JON 3:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah4:2\">JON 4:2</a></p>\n<h3>His patience</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num14:18\">NUM 14:18</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh9:30\">NEH 9:30</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet3:9\">2PE 3:9</a></p>\n<h3>His mercy</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh9:31\">NEH 9:31</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job9:15\">JOB 9:15</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps78:38\">PSA 78:38</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic7:18\">MIC 7:18</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ continues God's work as judge</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:22\">JHN 5:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:27\">JHN 5:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:42\">ACT 10:42</a></p>\n<h2>God will act as judge on the last day</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev20:12\">REV 20:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa2:17\">ISA 2:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph1:14-Zeph1:18\">ZEP 1:14–1:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:48\">JHN 12:48</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:31\">ACT 17:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom2:16\">ROM 2:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom14:10\">ROM 14:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor4:5\">1CO 4:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim4:1\">2TI 4:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet4:5\">1PE 4:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet2:9\">2PE 2:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet3:7\">2PE 3:7</a></p>",
